{"id":394425,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/知乎｜sars里的中国：一口不负责任的大锅/","date":"2015-06-03T07:29:57Z","modified":"2015-10-11T11:30:24Z","title":"知乎｜SARS里的中国：一口不负责任的大锅","content":"<p>问题： <a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/question/30844946/answer/49933868\">如何看待此次MERS事件中众多网民将非典期间处理作为正面例子进行赞扬？</a></p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-394430\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b.jpg\" alt=\"68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b\" width=\"315\" height=\"560\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/68c9e0157c7e4182a24e70fb7fd2cfaf_b-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 315px) 100vw, 315px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>答主：<a href=\"&quot;http://www.zhihu.com/people/willoughby\">Willoughby</a></strong></p>\n<blockquote><p>办砸了的事情，时间久了被人遗忘了也就罢了，竟然还能潜移默化变成吹嘘的资本。加上这次的翻船事件的种种花絮，我国真是有把丧事办成喜事、把灾难办成春节联欢晚会的优良传统。</p>\n<p>刚刚刚刚好，有一篇针对这个的打脸文，我给大家安利一下。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-394426\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国1.jpg\" alt=\"sars大国1\" width=\"397\" height=\"4623\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国1.jpg 397w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国1-88x1024.jpg 88w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 397px) 100vw, 397px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-394427\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/sars大国2.jpg\" alt=\"sars大国2\" width=\"397\" height=\"4802\" /></a><br />\n<a